headline: Sempra Infrastructure Partners Makes FID on Port Arthur LNG Phase 2
summary: The new phase will include two natural gas liquefaction trains, one LNG storage tank and associated facilities with a nameplate capacity of approximately 13 mtpa of U.S.-produced LNG.
